# Netlify redirects for canonical URL consistency

# Redirect www to non-www
https://www.forward-velocity.com/* https://forward-velocity.com/:splat 301!

# Ensure HTTPS
http://forward-velocity.com/* https://forward-velocity.com/:splat 301!
http://www.forward-velocity.com/* https://forward-velocity.com/:splat 301!

# Asset handling
/assets/*  /assets/:splat  200

# SPA fallback - this should be last
/*    /index.html   200
